#Install

  tar xzvf KXL-xxxx(xxxx is version)
  cd KXL-xxxx
  ./configure
  make
  make install
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
#Requirements
pulseaudio
libpulse-devel
libX11-devel
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Note: The sources use the euc-jp encoding. To use this encoding in Vim,
edit a file and then run this command to switch the encoding:
:edit ++encoding=euc-jp
